<div>
  <p>
    Hi
    {{name}},
  </p>

  <p>
    For added security, please use the following one-time password (OTP) to complete your sign-in to
    your
    {{appName}}
    account:
  </p>

  <p>
    Your OTP:
  </p>
  <p class='otp-wrapper'>
    <span id='otp' class='otp-field'>
      {{OTP}}
    </span>
  </p>
  <p>
    This OTP is valid for
    {{validationPeriod}}. If you did not request this OTP, please ignore this email and ensure your
    account is secure.
  </p>
  <p>
    Thank you for helping us keep your account safe!
  </p>

  <p>
    Best regards,
    <br />
    The
    {{appName}}
    Team
  </p>
</div>